  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This mixed methods study aims to answer the question: &quot;What is the work of being a patient
      with type 2 diabetes mellitus?&quot; .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will describe how much time persons with type 2 diabetes mellitus spend on health
      management and the burden they experience from these activities.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
